  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2c498bc80140a7345a14c2bde25d1b29, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dialog_Keanu
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CharacterDialogSetSO
  character: 2
  blocks:
  - context: 0
    lines:
    - So the exile finally reaches my jungle...
    - Every shadow here belongs to me!
  - context: 6
    lines:
    - Patience is a weapon...
    - Listen to the leaves. They tell you where danger is...
  - context: 2
    lines:
    - Watch the pattern, then move in one clean sequence.
    - Some branches are safe. Others will betray your weight.
  - context: 3
    lines:
    - "You\u2019re exposed. Step into the bushes if you want to live."
    - "If you attack from the open too often, I\u2019ll answer from the dark."
  - context: 7
    lines:
    - "The shadows\u2026 failed me"
    - "You learned\u2026 too quickly"
